{"id":165553,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/07/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-201175/","date":"2011-07-06T02:00:26Z","modified":"2011-07-08T20:45:52Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/7/5","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洛杉矶时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jun/29/opinion/la-oe-gardner-mao-vuitton-20110629\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">毛泽东、孔夫子和路易威登</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在毛泽东占据的天安门广场上，孔子神秘失踪，路易威登闪亮登场</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华尔街日报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.wsj.com/chinarealtime/2011/07/05/repress-or-reform-with-protests-on-rise-beijing-faces-choice/?mod=WSJBlog\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">压制还是改革：随着抗议增加，北京面临抉择</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——虽然目前尚无迹象表明会出现全国性的抗议运动，但政府还是担心中东局面在中国上演</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110705/wl_asia_afp/chinaunrestxinjianganniversary\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新疆骚乱两周年到来前夕，大赦国际指责中国镇压</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国不仅压制当地的不满声音，而且利用影响力让他在境外们噤声。”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/china-pledges-to-boost-restive-xinjiangs-economy-ahead-of-2-year-anniversary-of-deadly-riots/2011/07/04/gHQA7WedxH_story.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">骚乱将近两年后，中国保证提高新疆的经济水平</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——自治区主席白克力称要加大与周边国家经贸往来，并建设经济特区</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">世界社会主义者网站：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.wsws.org/articles/2011/jul2011/pers-j05.shtml\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中共庆祝成立</span>90<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">周年</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——没想到世界社会主义人士对中共如此厌恶：“中共的竭力鼓吹也难掩其资本主义矛盾”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/flashpoints-blog/2011/06/27/chinas-carrier-a-new-lexington/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的航母是否只是纯粹的训练舰？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国二战后的航母训练舰分为三代，中国的这艘航母大概相当于美国的第一代训练舰</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/flashpoints-blog/2011/07/04/big-week-for-china-air-power/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国空中实力大爆新闻的一周</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——回顾上周关于中国无人机和中国军用飞机开发人员的一些新闻报道</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>CNN</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://business.blogs.cnn.com/2011/07/04/happy-dependence-day-america-love-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国，祝你“依赖”节快乐！</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国昔日从英国的独立，演变成今日对中国的依赖：</span><span>97%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的庆祝焰火，</span><span>88%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的美国国旗都来自中国</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/flashpoints-blog/2011/06/24/working-with-china-at-nsg/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在核能供应团体中与中国进行合作</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——这个不为人所知的核技术出口控制团体，对于核扩散问题有着重要影响</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110705/ap_on_re_as/as_philippines_china_disputed_islands\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">菲律宾禁止一位中国外交官参加会议</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国使馆一秘与菲方讨论南沙群岛问题时“嗓门过高”，菲外交部告诉使馆以后不得再派他来与菲方会谈</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经贸动向】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110705/bs_afp/chinauseuwtotradedisputecommodities\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">世贸组织称中国限制原材料出口属于违法</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——要求中国采取措施，履行世贸成员国义务</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/06/world/asia/06china.html?partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国承认海上石油泄漏</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——最早的泄漏在六月初即已出现，但中海油到七月才开发布会通报此事</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110705/wl_asia_afp/chinaoilenvironment\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的漏油事故很可能产生长期影响</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——东海石油泄漏事故被隐瞒了几个星期才得到曝光，很可能对当地渔业造成破坏</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-07-05/china-said-to-discuss-letting-sec-probe-mainland-companies.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国称将讨论是否允许美国证券交易委员会到大陆对中国公司进行调查</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国在美上市公司近期的丑闻所带来的后果之一</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>eWeek</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eweek.com/c/a/Desktops-and-Notebooks/Microsofts-Baidu-Partnership-Could-Court-Controversy-161762/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">微软</span>&#8211;<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">百度的合作很可能引发争议</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——必应为百度提供英文搜索结果，但是它是否也会对结果进行过滤和审查？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">柳州老外：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://liuzhou.blog-city.com/rongan.htm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">要钱还是要命？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——最让我感觉到“中国式社会主义”是个彻头彻尾谎言的地方，就是中国的地方医院</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交学者：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/07/05/guo-meimei-and-the-red-cross/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">郭美美和红十字会</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——有人认为这位炫富女是反腐英雄，但更多人在想着怎么才能把捐给红十字会的钱要回来。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">条条大路通中国：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.allroadsleadtochina.com/2011/07/04/being-country-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在中国当“老土”</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“土”这个词可以很亲昵，也可以很侮辱。最“土”的人其实是那些炫富者。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">经济事务：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.econmatters.com/2011/07/college-graduates-too-many-in-china-not.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大学毕业生：中国太多了，美国太少了？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中美两国的高等教育各有各的问题</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">法新社：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/afp/20110705/wl_asia_afp/chinaunrestblast\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上海警方抓获在商场制造爆炸的嫌疑人</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——官方通报没有提及犯罪动机，但各地官员都对公众的不满情绪感到不安</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/international-news/global-exchange/chinas-women-show-taste-for-fast-cars-and-whisky/article2086792/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国女性青睐跑车和威士忌</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——而中国男性喜欢包包和美容产品……</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><i>如果您的iPad可以翻墙，请点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>即可看到最新译文；如果您的iPhone可以翻墙，请点击<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/?m=1\">这里</a>并加入书签；如果您的电脑可以翻墙，请到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\">这里</a>的左栏参加我们的一个小调查</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-5633661083013101096?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":473,"categories":[1],"tags":[11248,8840,17107]}